The human turn records the message, but the anima turn's `takeTurnStreaming` call doesn't pass the message along. Then `assembleConsultMessage` sees no `request.message`, no topic, returns `undefined`. Let me check how the Animator handles an undefined prompt to confirm this is the full picture.

